features.feature: 本次升级为您推出全新MagicOS 9.0版本，系统焕新升级，带来更流畅、更好玩、更智慧、更高效、更安全的全新体验，推荐您更新。
• 新增按压冲量动效，在桌面、负一屏、全局搜索、通知控制中心等交互场景，随手一按，处处能响应。 • 新增咔哒动效，在通知中心、桌面拖动应用到文件夹等场景，实现愉悦舒适的完成感。 • 优化划入负一屏、截屏等场景动效，实现整体效果的一致性。
• 新增AI重构编译引擎，全面提升应用启动速度和稳定性，实现又快又稳的流畅体验。 • 优化开机系统负载，提升版本升级、重启后性能流畅体验。
• 焕新桌面设计，全新设计的图标、卡片样式、控制中心，带来耳目一新的美学体验。 • 升级系统视觉风格，更新日历、笔记等应用的色彩和布局设计，使系统更美观、更好用。 • 升级天气时钟卡片，提供色彩丰富、灵动鲜活的个性化选择，带来具有生命力的视觉感知。
• 新增锁屏AI扩图功能，智能优化锁屏壁纸构图。体验路径：设置-桌面和个性化-锁屏样式-选择照片-双指捏合缩放图片-点击右下角弹出的AI扩图按钮。 • 新增锁屏AI风格功能，使能多样的锁屏壁纸创意风格。体验路径：设置-桌面和个性化-锁屏样式-AI风格。
• 新增基于多模态大模型的全新交互，支持图片问答和文档问答；唤醒YOYO助理发送图片或文档、拖拽图片或文档到任意门一步开启YOYO助理问答。
• 交互升级，指关节敲击并画圈，任意门自动打开，一步直达所需服务，意图识别更懂你，服务推荐更精准。 • 扩展服务场景，新增音乐、阅读、汽车搜索及翻译等服务，意图识别更丰富，体验更便捷。
• 扩展灵动胶囊使用场景，新增短时天气提醒、AI换脸检测、荣耀分享等，提升全局触达体验，重要信息不错过。
• 新增AI会议纪要功能，支持AI一键生成会议纪要；会议录制新增外语和方言识别能力，在文本笔记中新建录音即可体验。 • 新增智慧摘要和智慧排版功能，智能生成笔记摘要，快速了解笔记要点，一键排版笔记内容，提升笔记可读性。体验路径：笔记-新建文本笔记-AI笔记-智慧摘要/智慧排版。
•新增辅助阅读功能，支持多文对比，快速总结多方观点，一键生成思维导图，高效输出论文框架。 • 新增辅助写作功能，支持智慧润色、扩充/缩短篇幅、风格改写、智慧排版，轻松完成内容创作。体验路径：荣耀文档-打开一篇文档-AI文档。
• 新增AI扩图功能，支持旋转扩图和自由比例扩图，让照片秒变大片。体验路径：图库-选择照片-AI编辑-魔法修图-AI扩图。
• 新增AI风格功能，使能多样的创意风格，让照片重焕新生。体验路径：图库-选择照片-AI编辑-魔法修图-AI风格。
• 新增闭眼修复功能。体验路径：图库-选择照片-AI编辑-魔法修图-人脸修复-闭眼修复。
• 新增AI换脸检测功能，视频通话时自动识别对方AI换脸风险，为您的安全保驾护航。体验路径：设置-安全-反诈防护-视频通话AI换脸提醒。
• 新增游戏弹幕功能，支持微信、QQ等应用消息通知，可随心设置游戏弹幕的底色、字体颜色、弹幕速度等，游戏时重要消息不错过。体验路径：游戏管家-弹幕通知。
• 新增个人热点网络共享二维码，分享更便捷。体验路径：设置-移动网络-个人热点-开启个人热点-二维码连接。 • 新增个人热点自动关闭功能，可自由选择热点自动关闭时长。体验路径：设置-移动网络-个人热点-更多共享设置-热点自动关闭。

1、新版本下载及安装过程会消耗部分电量及轻微发热，属于正常现象。 2、版本安装后重启期间会做部分系统优化，预计花费1~3分钟，请耐心等待。 3、升级完成后部分系统优化会在后台自动进行，期间设备可能会出现耗电量增加、轻微发热、卡顿或充电慢等情况， 2~3 天后可恢复正常，建议升级完成后空闲时将平板灭屏充电1~2小时以上，以保证设备快速优化完成，请放心使用。 4、因部分第三方应用与Android 15不兼容，更新后可能会出现第三方应用无法正常使用的情况（如闪退、卡顿、耗电等）。建议您在应用市场尝试将该应用更新至最新版本，若仍无法解决问题，请您耐心等待应用更新信息，并及时更新。 5、请务必确保平板有10GB以上的内部存储空间，否则会有升级失败的风险。（查看存储空间方法：设置->存储）。 6、本次更新不会删除您的用户数据，但仍建议您在更新前做好数据备份。 7、如果您在使用过程中遇到任何问题，请访问“我的荣耀”应用或访问荣耀官方服务网站 https://www.honor.com/cn/contact-us 寻求支持。
The brand-new MagicOS 9.0 features a comprehensive refresh that offers a smoother, smarter, and safer experience. It is recommended to update.

• Touch-feedback animation ensures a responsive experience across various interactive scenarios, including the home screen, HonorBoard, global search, Notification Center and Control Center. • Snap animation brings you a comfortable sense of completion in scenarios such as dragging apps from Notification Center or the home screen to folders. • The optimized animation for entering HonorBoard and taking screenshots achieves consistency in the overall effect.

• AI restructures the compilation engine, comprehensively boosting app startup speed and stability, enabling more stable and smoother operations. • The optimized system load at startup enhances the performance after version upgrades and restarts.

• Newly designed icons, cards, and Control Center bring you a refreshing aesthetic experience. • Refreshed color schemes and layout design for apps, such as Calendar and Notes, enhance the system's aesthetics and usability. • New Weather and Clock card offers colorful and vivid options, delivering a vibrant visual perception.

• AI Outpainting intelligently optimizes the composition of lock screen wallpapers. Experience it by going to: Settings > Home screen and style > Lock screen style > Select photo > Pinch with two fingers to zoom in/out > Tap AI Outpainting button that pops up in the bottom right corner. • AI Style enables a variety of creative lock screen wallpapers. Experience it by going to: Settings > Home screen and style > Lock screen style > AI Style.

• The new interaction, powered by a multimodal large model, allows for queries involving images and documents. To get started, just wake up YOYO Assistant and send images or documents, or you can drag and drop items into Magic Portal.

• Knock and draw a circle with your knuckle, Magic Portal automatically opens and provides direct access to the needed service. It can intelligently recognize your intention, recommending more personalized services. • Intention recognition now covers more scenarios, such as music, reading, car search, and translation services, making operations more convenient.

• Magic Capsule now supports more scenarios, including short-term weather alerts, AI Face-Swapping Scam Protection, and HONOR Share. This expansion allows for an improved global reach experience, ensuring that no important information is missed.

• AI Minutes allows you to generate meeting minutes with a single tap. Meeting recording now includes foreign language and dialect recognition capabilities. You can experience it by creating a new audio recording in text notes. • AI Summary can intelligently generate note summaries, and AI Format allows you to format text with a single tap. You can read the notes more easily and quickly grasp the key points. Try it out by going to: Notes > New typed note > AI Notes > AI Summary/AI Format.

• Assisted reading supports comparison of multiple texts and quick summarization of diverse viewpoints. Furthermore, it can generate mind maps with a single tap, and efficiently produce paper frameworks. • Assisted writing now features AI text refinement, Expand/Shorten text, Change writing styles, and AI Format, making your content creation smoother. Try it out by going to: HONOR Docs > Open a document > AI Doc.
• AI Outpainting enhances photo composition by allowing rotation or adjustment in a free ratio. Try it out by going to: Gallery > Select a photo > AI Edit > Magic Retouch > AI Outpainting.
• AI Style offers a variety of creative styles to give your photos a new look. Try it out by going to: Gallery > Select a photo > AI Edit > Magic Retouch > AI Style.
• Eyes Open can be used for image editing. Try it out by going to: Gallery > Select an image > AI Edit > Magic Retouch > Face tune > Eyes Open.

• AI Face-Swapping Scam Protection automatically detects AI face swaps during video calls to safeguard your privacy. Experience it by going to: Settings > Security and privacy > Scam Protection > AI face swap alert for video calls.

• On-screen comments in games show notifications from apps like WeChat or QQ, ensuring you do not miss any important messages. You can freely customize the background color, font color, and speed of the on-screen comments. Experience it by going to: Game Manager > Bullet notifications.

• Conveniently share personal hotspot via a QR code. Experience it by going to: Settings > Mobile network > Personal hotspot > Turn it on > Scan to connect. • Set a duration of inactivity for personal hotspot, and it will automatically switch off if this period is exceeded. Experience it by going to: Settings > Mobile network > Personal hotspot > More > Duration.

1. The download and installation process of the new version will consume some battery power and cause slight heating, which is normal. 2. During the restart after the installation, some system optimizations will be performed, expected to take 1~3 minutes. Please be patient. 3. After the upgrade is completed, some system optimizations will automatically proceed in the background. During this period, the device may experience increased power consumption, slight heating, lagging, or slow charging. It can be restored to normal after 2~3 days. It is recommended to charge the tablet with the screen off for more than 1~2 hours after the upgrade is completed to ensure rapid optimization of the device. Please use it with confidence. 4. Some third-party apps may not be compatible with Android 15 and may malfunction after the update (such as crush, lag, abnormal power consumption). Please update your apps to the latest version in App Market. If the problems persist, please wait for upcoming app updates. 5. Please make sure your tablet has more than 10GB of free space, or the update may fail. (To check your storage space, go to Settings > Storage). 6. This update will not affect your personal data, but it is recommended to back up your data before updating. 7. If you encounter any problem during use, you can get our support by going to My HONOR or visiting our website at https://www.honor.com/cn/contact-us.
